lhach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Harmani Camlhach</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://people.we.mediaone.net/aratar/note.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#b87333>1/14/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#b87333>9:30:00 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><A HREF=http://pub43.ezboard.com/fcodeofhonorofficialboardfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Reply</FONT></A><BR><img src=http://people.we.mediaone.net/aratar/harmani.jpg border=0></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">It is about time</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">While I have mixed reviews on this idea, I am mostly glad they are eliminating the exp penalty for hybrids, but I wish they would have done it when it would have benefitted me more.  Oh well, it probably won't effect bards anyways since we are only hybrids when it is in the best interest to Verant.<br>
